Preoperative prediction model to evaluate salvage surgery in patients with 
recurrent or second primary oral cavity squamous cell carcinoma.

Lu HJ(1), Peng CY(2), Tseng HC(3), Hsin CH(4), Chuang CY(4), Chen CC(5), Huang 
WS(1), Chiu YW(6), Yang SF(7).

