"We are never taught anything about the elderly." Establishing the gap in 
elderly health care competencies in nursing education in Uganda.

Nawagi F(1), Mukisa J(2), Najjuma JN(3), Nabirye RC(4).

Author information:
(1)Makerere University College of Health Sciences (MaKCHS), School of Medicine, 
Kampala, Uganda. fnawagi@gmail.com.
(2)Makerere University College of Health Sciences (MaKCHS), School of Biomedical 
Sciences, Kampala, Uganda.
(3)Mbarara University of Science and Technology (MUST), Faculty of Medicine, 
