Harnessing new mHealth technologies to Strengthen the Management of 
Multidrug-Resistant Tuberculosis in Vietnam (V-SMART trial): a protocol for a 
randomised controlled trial.

Velen K(1), Nguyen VN(2), Nguyen BH(2), Dang T(3), Nguyen HA(4), Vu DH(4), Do 
